<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.5.6">
<l>kariya mēṉimicai veḷiya nīṟuciṟi tēyiṭum</l>
<l>periya kōlat taṭaṅkaṇṇaṉ viṇṇōr perumāṉṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>uriya collā licaimālaika ḷēttiyuḷḷap peṟṟēṟku</l>
<l>ariya tuṇṭō veṉakkiṉṟu toṭṭumiṉi yeṉṟumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Kṛṣṇa with big beautiful long eyes who places just a little white ash</l>
<l>on his black body, the great lord of the celestials,</l>
<l>praising him in a musical garland with befitting words, for me who obtains [him in my] heart,</l>
<l>will there be anything difficult for me from today on, now [or] ever?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
